{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/yubikey-5c-nfc/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"p3t.lu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ffcd9142-7f1e-545e-b04c-9ae60e608576","excerpt":"觀望 YubiKey 很久了，在推特上不時會看到有人提到，google “YubiKey 用途” 找不到太多一眼看起來有用介紹，YouTube 也只有一些開箱評論，想了解真實生活中的 use cases，一直對 YubiKey 的使用情境充滿著好奇與幻想，剛好有朋友揪省運費就…www (結果後來沒成團 XD…","html":"<p>觀望 YubiKey 很久了，在推特上不時會看到有人提到，google “YubiKey 用途” 找不到太多一眼看起來有用介紹，YouTube 也只有一些開箱評論，想了解真實生活中的 use cases，一直對 YubiKey 的使用情境充滿著好奇與幻想，剛好有朋友揪省運費就…www (結果後來沒成團 XD) 但一直止不住我的好奇心，所以最後還是決定 solo 親身體驗一下了 :p</p>\n<p>8/14 Amazon US 下單<br>\n8/24 TPE 到貨</p>\n<p>期間每天想到就會刷一下追蹤包裹頁面看貨到哪了，很期待著到貨，ETA 是 8/27 最後比預計的到貨時間早了三天。</p>\n<p>收到一個牛皮紙袋\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/d2602/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yubikey 5c nfc 0\"\n        title=\"yubikey 5c nfc 0\"\n        src=\"/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/ff44c/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 158w,\n/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/a6688/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 315w,\n/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 630w,\n/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/0ede0/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 945w,\n/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/3ac88/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 1260w,\n/static/c83195f0bd18a9fb6ee2cafff0e05452/d2602/yubikey-5c-nfc-0.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>內容物 YubiKey 5C NFC\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/9568a/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yubikey 5c nfc 1\"\n        title=\"yubikey 5c nfc 1\"\n        src=\"/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/ff44c/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 158w,\n/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/a6688/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 315w,\n/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 630w,\n/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/0ede0/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 945w,\n/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/3ac88/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 1260w,\n/static/d72b39063fffeb516aa9363a3699c4e9/9568a/yubikey-5c-nfc-1.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>因為 8/23 剛打完疫苗，接下來的三天副作用讓我的手無法使用… 稍微恢復後才挑了個夜晚開始了我的 YubiKey 之旅。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>首先，當然是爬了官網上的 <a href=\"https://www.yubico.com/tw/works-with-yubikey/catalog/\">Works with YubiKey catalog</a> 一輪，把自己有用的服務都試著設定看看，然後試一下它們是怎麼運作的，一開始還以為大家都會是一樣的行為，沒想到不同的服務跟 yubico 整合上也有些差異，試了一輪之後覺得 Microsoft 整合的好棒，真的是有感的方便！</p>\n<p>有插著 YubiKey 的情況下會多出 “Sign in with a security key” 的選項，按了之後連原本的帳號密碼都不用打就可以直接登入了！(當然 YubiKey 還有設了一個 PIN 保護著)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/f1901/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.30379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yubikey 5c nfc 4\"\n        title=\"yubikey 5c nfc 4\"\n        src=\"/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/f058b/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/c26ae/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png 158w,\n/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/6bdcf/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png 315w,\n/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/f058b/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png 630w,\n/static/f34fe9b8425c236c32773269dddeea63/f1901/yubikey-5c-nfc-4.png 942w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>因為本身有在用 GPG 所以參考了 <a href=\"https://support.yubico.com/hc/en-us/articles/360013790259-Using-Your-YubiKey-with-OpenPGP\">Using Your YubiKey with OpenPGP</a> 把我的 GPG key 放進 YubiKey 裡，然後參考了 <a href=\"https://medium.com/@SSWilsonKao/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8-mac-%E4%B8%8A-%E6%8A%8A-yubikey-%E8%88%87-gpg-ssh-%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7-5f842d20ad6a\">如何在 Mac 上，把 YubiKey 與 GPG、SSH 搭配在一起</a> 和 <a href=\"https://github.com/herlo/ssh-gpg-smartcard-config\">SSH authentication using a GPG smart card</a> 讓 YubiKey、GPG 及 SSH 做了整合！</p>\n<p>BTW, 本文的 commit 就是透過 YubiKey 用裡面的 GPG key 簽名並透過 GPG 匯出的 SSH key 推上 GitHub 的！\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/c50e3/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAATUlEQVQI15XMyRFAQAAAQbFg78teagtF/lGNFHj0t6etH/hyIF1lVvGXxSSkr+i4o0JjtZnpvC9MGkhXEDZ/z3RChIzdBr4/uHKifOMFvCA795DaOq8AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yubikey 5c nfc 3\"\n        title=\"yubikey 5c nfc 3\"\n        src=\"/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/f058b/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/c26ae/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 158w,\n/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/6bdcf/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 315w,\n/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/f058b/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 630w,\n/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/40601/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 945w,\n/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/78612/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 1260w,\n/static/dd8266d7f56a513802a549dab0e0b3ab/c50e3/yubikey-5c-nfc-3.png 2442w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>當然我也試了 <a href=\"https://www.yubico.com/products/yubico-authenticator/\">Yubico Authenticator</a>，把 YubiKey 放在 iPhone 頭上感應解鎖的確是蠻潮的，多加一層保護也肯定是更安全，但 App 體感沒 Authy 那麼好用… 而且方便性又下降了一些，所以目前是沒有強烈的理由要把 App 2FA 的服務轉移過來，再觀望觀望吧。</p>\n<p>最後附上我的 YubiKey 5C NFC 獨照\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/9568a/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yubikey 5c nfc 2\"\n        title=\"yubikey 5c nfc 2\"\n        src=\"/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/ff44c/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 158w,\n/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/a6688/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 315w,\n/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/828fb/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 630w,\n/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/0ede0/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 945w,\n/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/3ac88/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 1260w,\n/static/b32f0e2d17cc742c0bdcaa6a3ef494a6/9568a/yubikey-5c-nfc-2.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h4>2021/11/28 update</h4>\n<p>因為月初離職之前慣用的 MacBook 還給前公司，變成要跟家人共用一台 ThinkPad，還好之前有把常用的網路服務登入加上 YubiKey, 這時候就顯得超級方便！插上電腦就可以登入了，不用去回想密碼是哪一組！再來現在公司 MacBook 上登入我個人的網路服務也是用這把 YubiKey，真的是非常之愉悅 XD</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"YubiKey 5C NFC","date":"August 26, 2021","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/shell-welcome-message/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Shell 的歡迎訊息(welcome message)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/iphone-sleep-analytics/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"iPhone 睡眠分析"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"ffcd9142-7f1e-545e-b04c-9ae60e608576","previousPostId":"6a86e991-7f2c-5fbc-9dda-110243b66d2b","nextPostId":"a5e57af9-3d28-517c-83fd-752af5d0a142"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3624854548","548598555"]}